Rapper Sho Madjozi is best known for her natural, vibrant and colourful braids. Now, the Rapper is letting her own hair breathe and, we have to say, Sho sure does have inches! She shared a video on Twitter of her sporting her natural hair and sharing some hair-care tips and isnpiring some ladies to share their natural hair journey too! Her post read: “A huge part of hair growth is genetics, but how you treat your hair can make a difference. 3 years of gentle braiding, moisturising and minimal heat.”In another tweet, the star posted a video of her cornrows, which she will wear for a few days.One of her fans asked what she meant by “gentle” braiding, to which she responded: “I don't allow my hair to be pulled at all. It's always done quite loose.” 